ily. Along with her husband, she is ecstatic to call 3 amazing little people her children. She also enjoys a good workout, the kind that leaves a puddle of sweat around you and grasping for air.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"History Section\" _builder_version=\"4.16\" background_color=\"#ceac58\" custom_padding=\"1px||1px||true|\" border_color_all=\"#000dff\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.16\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.16\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.16\" text_font=\"Sorts Mill Goudy||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"52px\" text_line_height=\"1em\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Improving the lives of small business owners</em></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.16\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.16\" text_font=\"Open Sans||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_font_size=\"95px\" text_line_height=\"1em\" text_orientation=\"center\" animation_style=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"left\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>10<sup style=\"font-size: 50px;\">+</sup> YEARS</strong></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" admin_label=\"About Section\" _builder_version=\"4.16\" module_alignment=\"right\" custom_padding=\"30px||0px||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||120px|\" custom_padding_phone=\"\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"3_4,1_4\" _builder_version=\"4.16\" custom_margin=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding=\"|||\" animation_style=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"right\" animation_intensity_slide=\"1%\" locked=\"off\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"3_4\" _builde