_version=\"4.16\" custom_padding=\"|||\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.16\" text_font=\"||||||||\" header_font=\"||||||||\" header_2_font=\"Sorts Mill Goudy||||||||\" header_2_font_size=\"42px\" header_2_line_height=\"1.4em\" custom_margin=\"||20px|\" header_2_font_size_tablet=\"36px\" header_2_font_size_phone=\"\" header_2_font_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>As a tax business owner, having a team of advisors with the upmost integrity to help clients achieve their business and personal goals is of upmost importance.</span></h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_divider color=\"#29cb8b\" divider_weight=\"3px\" _builder_version=\"4.16\" max_width=\"50px\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][/et_pb_divider][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.16\" text_font=\"||||||||\" text_font_size=\"16px\" text_line_height=\"2em\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span> Frieda was born and raised in Togo, West Africa. She migrated to the United States upon graduating High School for College. Her parents made tremendous sacrifices to send her to the United States for higher education in order to avail her with opportunities they didn’t have. She landed in Michigan and wasted no time. Frieda worked hard to achieve her goals, overcoming the challenges of mastering a new language, cultural shocks and tremendous homesickness especially through the hard, cold and long Michigan winters. She earned a Bachelor’s and Master’s degrees from Eastern Michigan University and best of all for a fraction of the cost and totally debt free.</span></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>Upon graduating with her Master\'s in Accounting, Frieda spent a decade working at a public accounting firm and various private industries. Frieda is a number nerd. She loves helping people. She is thrilled to be able to use her talents along with her education and experience t